synopsis: Surrealistic flashbacks of our horrid exposed past.
After unknowingly cheating death, a teenager meets the grim reaper, who gives him 52 hours to live.
tagline: There are always ways to be remembered.

synopsis: A group of families on a tropical holiday discover that the secluded beach where they are staying is somehow causing them to age rapidly – reducing their entire lives into a single day.
tagline: It's only a matter of time.
